{"id":799,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":799,"title":"Jeremiah 30","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 30"],[".studySummary",["i","In the last days, Judah and Israel will be gathered to their own lands—David, their king (the Messiah), will reign over them."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.1","order":"02.25.030.52910"},["b","1"],"The word that came to Jeremiah from the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.2","order":"02.25.030.52911"},["b","2"],"Thus speaketh the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of Israel, saying, Write thee all the words that I have spoken unto thee in a book."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.3","order":"02.25.030.52912"},["b","3"],"For, lo, the days come, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that I will bring again the captivity of my people",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Israel"],"and Judah, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": and I will cause them to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"return"],"to the land that I gave to their fathers, and they shall possess it."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.4","order":"02.25.030.52913"},["b","4"],"¶And these",["i","are"],"the words that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake concerning Israel and concerning Judah."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.5","order":"02.25.030.52914"},["b","5"],"For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; We have heard a voice of trembling, of fear, and not of peace."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.6","order":"02.25.030.52915"},["b","6"],"Ask ye now, and see whether a man doth travail with child? wherefore do I see every man with his hands on his loins, as a woman in travail, and all faces are turned into paleness?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.7","order":"02.25.030.52916"},["b","7"],"Alas! for that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"day"],["i","is"],"great, so that none",["i","is"],"like it: it",["i","is"],"even the time of Jacob’s trouble; but he shall be saved out of it."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.8","order":"02.25.030.52917"},["b","8"],"For it shall come to pass in that day, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts,",["i","that"],"I will break his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"yoke"],"from off thy neck, and will burst thy bonds, and strangers shall no more",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"serve themselves of him"],":"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.9","order":"02.25.030.52918"},["b","9"],"But they shall serve the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"their God, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"David"],"their king, whom I will raise up unto them."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.10","order":"02.25.030.52919"},["b","10"],"¶Therefore fear thou not, O my servant Jacob, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; neither be dismayed, O Israel: for, lo, I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"save"],"thee from afar, and thy seed from the land of their captivity; and Jacob shall return, and shall be in rest, and be quiet, and none shall make",["i","him"],"afraid."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.11","order":"02.25.030.52920"},["b","11"],"For I",["i","am"],"with thee, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", to save thee: though I make a full",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"end"],"of all nations whither I have scattered thee, yet will I not make a full end of thee: but I will correct thee in measure, and will not leave thee altogether unpunished."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.12","order":"02.25.030.52921"},["b","12"],"For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Thy"],"bruise",["i","is"],"incurable,",["i","and"],"thy wound",["i","is"],"grievous."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.13","order":"02.25.030.52922"},["b","13"],["i","There is"],"none to plead thy cause, that thou mayest be bound up: thou hast no healing medicines."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.14","order":"02.25.030.52923"},["b","14"],"All thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"lovers"],"have forgotten thee; they seek thee not; for I have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"wounded thee"],"with the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"wound"],"of an enemy, with the chastisement of a",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"cruel"],"one, for the multitude of thine",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_14e"},"iniquity"],";",["i","because"],"thy sins were increased."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.15","order":"02.25.030.52924"},["b","15"],"Why criest thou for thine affliction?",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"thy"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"sorrow"],["i","is"],"incurable for the multitude of thine iniquity:",["i","because"],"thy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"sins"],"were increased, I have done these things unto thee."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.16","order":"02.25.030.52925"},["b","16"],"Therefore all they that devour thee shall be devoured; and all thine adversaries, every one of them, shall go into captivity; and they that spoil thee shall be a spoil, and all that prey upon thee will I give for a prey."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.17","order":"02.25.030.52926"},["b","17"],"For I will restore",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"health"],"unto thee, and I will heal thee of thy wounds, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; because they called thee an Outcast,",["i","saying,"],"This",["i","is"],"Zion, whom no man seeketh after."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.18","order":"02.25.030.52927"},["b","18"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; Behold, I will bring again the captivity of Jacob’s tents, and have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"mercy"],"on his dwellingplaces; and the city shall be builded upon her own heap, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"the"],"palace shall remain after the manner thereof."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.19","order":"02.25.030.52928"},["b","19"],"And out of them shall proceed thanksgiving and the voice of them that make merry: and I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"multiply"],"them, and they shall not be few; I will also glorify them, and they shall not be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"small"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.20","order":"02.25.030.52929"},["b","20"],"Their children also shall be as aforetime, and their congregation shall be established before me, and I will punish all that oppress them."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.21","order":"02.25.030.52930"},["b","21"],"And their nobles shall be of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"themselves"],", and their governor shall proceed from the midst of them; and I will cause him to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"draw near"],", and he shall approach unto me: for who",["i","is"],"this that engaged his heart to approach unto me? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.22","order":"02.25.030.52931"},["b","22"],"And ye shall be my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"people"],", and I will be your God."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.23","order":"02.25.030.52932"},["b","23"],"Behold, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"whirlwind"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"goeth forth with fury, a continuing whirlwind: it shall fall with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"pain"],"upon the head of the wicked."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.24","order":"02.25.030.52933"},["b","24"],"The fierce anger of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall not return, until he have done",["i","it,"],"and until he have performed the intents of his heart: in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"latter days"],"ye shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"consider it"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.3a","order":"02.25.030.52934"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-twelve-tribes-of"},"TG Israel, Twelve Tribes of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.3b","order":"02.25.030.52936"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-gathering-of"},"TG Israel, Gathering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.7a","order":"02.25.030.52938"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.11"},"Joel 2:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/4.5"},"Mal. 4:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.8a","order":"02.25.030.52940"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bondage-physical"},"TG Bondage, Physical"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bondage-spiritual"},"Bondage, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.8b","order":"02.25.030.52942"},["b","8b"],["span.small","OR"],"enslave, or exploit him."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.9a","order":"02.25.030.52944"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/23.5.5-6"},"Jer. 23:5 (5–6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/34.24.23-24"},"Ezek. 34:24 (23–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/37.24.24-25"},"37:24 (24–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.10a","order":"02.25.030.52946"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/13.9"},"Hosea 13:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.33"},"D&C 38:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.22"},"136:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.11a","order":"02.25.030.52948"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.8"},"Amos 9:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.9.1-9"},"D&C 101:9 (1–9)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-scattering-of"},"TG Israel, Scattering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.12a","order":"02.25.030.52950"},["b","12a"],["span.small","JST"],"Jer. 30:12–13 … thy bruise is",["i","not"],"incurable,",["i","although"],"thy",["i","wounds are"],"grievous.",["i","Is there"],"none to plead thy cause, that thou mayest be bound up",["i","? Hast thou"],"no healing medicines",["i","?"]],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.14a","order":"02.25.030.52952"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.2"},"Lam. 1:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.14b","order":"02.25.030.52954"},["b","14b"],["span.small","OR"],"caused thee to be wounded."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.14c","order":"02.25.030.52956"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/5.13"},"Hosea 5:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"14d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.14d","order":"02.25.030.52958"},["b","14d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cruelty"},"TG Cruelty"],"."],["div",{"id":"14e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.14e","order":"02.25.030.52960"},["b","14e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.5"},"Lam. 1:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.15a","order":"02.25.030.52962"},["b","15a"],["span.small","JST"],"Jer. 30:15 …",["i","Is"],"thy sorrow incurable",["i","?"],"…"],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.15b","order":"02.25.030.52964"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.12"},"Lam. 1:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.15c","order":"02.25.030.52966"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.2.1-9"},"D&C 101:2 (1–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.17a","order":"02.25.030.52968"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/health"},"TG Health"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.18a","order":"02.25.030.52970"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.9"},"D&C 101:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.18b","order":"02.25.030.52972"},["b","18b"],["span.small","HEB"],"the citadel shall stand in its right place."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.19a","order":"02.25.030.52974"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.58"},"D&C 45:58"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.19b","order":"02.25.030.52976"},["b","19b"],["span.small","OR"],"insignificant."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.21a","order":"02.25.030.52978"},["b","21a"],["span.small","OR"],"their own people."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.21b","order":"02.25.030.52980"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-presence-of"},"TG God, Presence of"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.22a","order":"02.25.030.52982"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.23"},"Hosea 2:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/13.9"},"Zech. 13:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.101"},"D&C 84:101"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.23a","order":"02.25.030.52984"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.6"},"D&C 63:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.23b","order":"02.25.030.52986"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pain"},"TG Pain"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.24a","order":"02.25.030.52988"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.16"},"Ezek. 38:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.24b","order":"02.25.030.52990"},["b","24b"],["span.small","HEB"],"fully understand this. See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.8"},"2 Ne. 25:8"],"."]]}
